data.description: Live your best life in this gorgeous 4000+ sqft 5BR/3BTH Whisper Creek log home! Situated on 3.55 acres in the coveted Aspen Glen subdivision, this magnificent property offers luxury living w/the serenity of Montana's great outdoors. Enjoy jaw-dropping views of the Whitefish Mountain Range and Therriault Pass while relaxing on the expansive back deck or on any of the home's multiple covered porches. Step inside and let the beauty of the natural landscape pour in through the floor-to-ceiling windows accented with 10' vaulted ceilings and wire-brushed RBM fir/larch flooring. The open floor plan highlights the modern design of the home and provides ample space for families and large groups to gather. The finished basement features a rec/game room w/media area, wet bar with kitchenette, 2 bedrooms and a 3/4-bath. The detached 2-car garage features a 425 sqft apartment that can be used for guest quarters. Call Gretchen Lancaster at 406-291-7099 or your real estate professional. Custom features modern country kitchen with hickory cabinets and oversized island, low-maintenance Pella EnduraClad® wood windows and doors, and red and blue pine. Enjoy the comforts of central heat and A/C, 3 propane/pellet stoves, a tankless water heater, lower and upper-level laundry and 5/8’ drywall for added soundproofing and fire protection. The oversized deck and stone patio feature the perfect setup for entertaining guests or putting your feet up after a long day. Cool off in the 800+ foot GLID stream access that meanders through the property, or enjoy the shared parkland and private walking paths of the Aspen Glen subdivision.
